metadata.description:
The Fountain of Shade lies deep inside the forest to the south of Elvendell. It seems to be constructed by the previous inhabitant of this land.

It is believed that upon bathing in the nearby spring, one can maintain their youthful body for a longer period of time. 

However, the source of the water remain a mystery.
